rows.label: tlk44310181_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Welcome to Teos Aure,
the Luxurian capital!

rows.label: tlk44310181_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Before, there were strict limits on
entering the country, but now those
rules are being relaxed.

rows.label: tlk44310181_02_msg0004
rows.name:
And even board games, which used to
be contraband until recently, are being
sold in the open! You should see it!
